{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day-- you may have seen this in the picture-- he didn't let them go home at night, because he knew there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was plenty going on in, in, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was, it was a bad time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, things got scarce.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and medical facilities, we had a, a hospital in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one, I think one of the last, last Aktions, they cleaned out the whole hospital of all patients and some of the doctors and just shot them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these are some of the things that went on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In between-- one day a week or so, I worked outside somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to work outside somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was almost like a holiday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you can smell some fresh air, you-- at the airfield, at the army airfield, you, you had to dig, dig up the field.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you went there by truck outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It, it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, [LAUGHS] you either have your spirits, or you don't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You hope.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You keep-- you just keep hope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You keep, you keep living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you, you try to have a normal life as much as-- I remember in the ghetto, there were young, young, a few young people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a teenager at that time, and boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a 9 o'clock curfew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got together after work, and we sat in a little room, and we sang songs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or if somebody had a record player, we'd play some, we'd play some records.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you do-- you do a little socializing within the limitations that the ghetto permitted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's how we kept up our, our spirits.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
